end of prologue:
generate department
set level 1
set title at 1
set performance at C
add the basic event deck

promotion function
remove promotion flag
adds one level
grabs new title
check if level 6 {
  add leveled events to deck
}

basic loop:
check if event is flagged {
  load event loop
  resolve event screens (apply changes along way) until conclusion reached
} else {
  check focus for effect {
    effect performance
  }
  check promotion flag or performance for promotion {
    promote
  }
  flag a new event from deck
}